name: Face EP
description:
First ever release from both Scum Killer and Vulsellum!
	5 tracks of Scottish Death Metal from Vulsellum who seem to be trapped in the early ‘90s with Carcass and Napalm Death!
	1. Carcass of the Dove
2. Face
3. Sheep In Wolves Clothing
4. Walk Away
5. Manufactured Apocalypse

name: Who This Way Comes?
description:
Welcome Home, Explorer have been locked in the practice room searching for their sound for around two years and after finding it, have come out all guns blazing!

This CD contains 4 tracks which are not very easy to categorise into a genre but to give you an indication of the sound, the band are influenced by Alexisonfire, Glassjaw, Dillinger Escape Plan, Fordirelifesake, The Fall of Troy and any other type of challenging or progressive yet melodic alternative music.

Tracklisting:

Adellande Letters
Peninsula
The Shadow Moses Incident
Verme y Sufrir (See Me and Suffer)
